                            "type": "text",
                            "break_line": true,
                            "content": "Search by typing multiple genes in the Search box. This can be done by inputting comma-separated gene symbols, for example, 'COL1A1,COL6A3,COL6A1' or use syntax 'genes=(COL1A1,COL6A3,COL6A1)'."
